abstract: It was telling that Wisconsin fans refrained from storming the field after the Badgers took apart the Huskers on Saturday night.
snippet: It was telling that Wisconsin fans refrained from storming the field after the Badgers took apart the Huskers on Saturday night.
lead_paragraph: MADISON, Wis. -- Perhaps the most notable part of Wisconsin's rout of Nebraska was the reaction of its fans. The Badger faithful stormed the field last season after the upset of Ohio State, but they kept their revelry to the stands Saturday night.
